## The Evergreen Principle

The robot never becomes obsolete because it is never finished.

- Age 8: school skin, learning personality, homework tools
- Age 15: different skin, different personality, different tools
- Age 25: moves out with them, adapts to adult life
- Age 40: home management tools, different again
- Age 60: companion mode, health monitoring, different again

Same skeleton. Whole life.

One sale. Generational revenue. Unbreakable loyalty.

