## Prior Art Statement

To the best of the author's knowledge, no existing humanoid
robotics platform combines:

- Skeleton-as-platform architecture with full modular ecosystem
- Free school distribution as primary R&D, data, and loyalty
  acquisition strategy
- Care refresh subscription as the primary recurring revenue vehicle
- Service interval as silent recall and upgrade deployment mechanism
- Evergreen design philosophy — one skeleton, whole life adaptation

as a unified business model and platform architecture.

